OL,3,CMan jailed for raping woman after
OL,4,Ctricking his way into her home
OL,6,FA man from Nottingham has been jailed
OL,7,Ffor 13 years after being found guilty
OL,8,Fof rape.
OL,10,FMarcus Bennett, 44, of Radcliffe Road,
OL,11,Ftricked his way into his victim's home
OL,12,Fin June this year before raping her.
OL,14,FThe victim, who cannot be identified
OL,15,Ffor legal reasons, also reported two
OL,16,Ffurther incidents when Bennett raped
OL,17,Fher as she slept.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
