PN,37702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1779719224
OL,3,CMan jailed for raping woman after
OL,4,Ctricking his way into her home
OL,6,FShe reported the first offence to her
OL,7,Fmother and sent her pictures of
OL,8,Fbruises, but had been too frightened
OL,9,Fof Bennett to report it to police.
OL,11,FThe victim reported Bennett to police
OL,12,Fin September after receiving a series
OL,13,Fof threatening messages from him.
OL,15,FBennett denied the allegations and
OL,16,Fsaid he was "vexed" if he was denied
OL,17,Fsex.
OL,26,@xD@MOUxD@SO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1779719224
OL,3,CMan jailed for raping woman after
OL,4,Ctricking his way into her home
OL,6,FIn response to a question about
OL,7,Fwhether someone could consent to sex
OL,8,Fif they were asleep, Bennett said he
OL,9,Fdidn't know, before later saying they
OL,10,Fcould not.
OL,12,FHe claimed not to have seen the victim
OL,13,Fat the time of the alleged offences,
OL,14,Fwhich was disproved by photo evidence
OL,15,Fshown to police. Later photo evidence
OL,16,Fproved his was not true.
OL,18,FFollowing a two-week trial at
OL,19,FNottingham Crown Court, Bennett was
OL,20,Ffound guilty of two counts of rape.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
