FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1779719224
OL,3,CMan jailed for raping woman after
OL,4,Ctricking his way into her home
OL,6,FHe was cleared of a third count of
OL,7,Frape.
OL,9,FBennett has been added to the sex
OL,10,Foffenders' register and handed a
OL,11,Frestraining order banning him from any
OL,12,Ffurther contact with the victim.
OL,14,FA spokesperson from Nottinghamshire
OL,15,FPolice, said:
OL,17,F"Like many victims of serious sexual
OL,18,Foffences, the victim in this case was
OL,19,Fconcerned that she would not be
OL,20,Fbelieved if she came forward and told
OL,21,Fthe police.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1779719224
OL,3,CMan jailed for raping woman after
OL,4,Ctricking his way into her home
OL,6,F"As this case demonstrates, we take
OL,7,Fall reports of this nature extremely
OL,8,Fseriously and will leave no stone
OL,9,Funturned in getting to the truth.
OL,11,F"When presented with the very
OL,12,Fcompelling account of the victim and
OL,13,Fthe other very strong evidence against
OL,14,FBennett, the jury in this case were
OL,15,Fclear in their verdict.
OL,17,F"I am delighted for the victim that
OL,18,Fjustice has now been done and pleased
OL,19,Fthat Bennett can pose no further
OL,20,Fthreat to her or other women."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU|D@^O]
